author: wsjcom
title: Martha Hunt Reveals What’s on Her iPhone
text:
Number of unread emails: This is embarrassing. I doubt anyone has me beat on this one! 66,436.
When do you feel compelled to charge your phone? I get that dying-phone-induced anxiety once my battery is at less than 20 percent. I had a case that charged my phone but it got ruined. Now I’m just living on the edge.
Most-used app: Twitter....
